name: Unlikely Combinations
description:
Made for Kenney Jam 2019 this game is all about matching a series of often interrelated images to complete your plan of what you need to do in order to finish a game in just a few days. 

Made in a very short time and using just Assets from kenney.nl and a few sounds and fonts this should be playable in browser by dragging and clicking

Uses Kenney Item pack, UI pack, UI Space pack, Backgrounds pack and particle pack.
